OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779062581
OL,3,CStarmer 'deciding whether to announce
OL,4,Cdeparture timetable'
OL,6,FThe very difficult decision being made
OL,7,Fby the prime minister at his Chequers
OL,8,Fretreat this weekend is whether he can
OL,9,Fre-assert his authority and re-
OL,10,Fenergise his government, despite
OL,11,Fknowing that if Burnham wins in
OL,12,FMakerfield he will be evicted - or
OL,13,Fwhether he would bring more stability
OL,14,Fto government by announcing a
OL,15,Ftimetable for a leadership election
OL,16,Fand his own departure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779062581
OL,3,CStarmer 'deciding whether to announce
OL,4,Cdeparture timetable'
OL,6,FThat is what his ministers tell me,
OL,7,Fthough they concede that on either
OL,8,Fcourse government will lose momentum,
OL,9,Fat least till it's known whether
OL,10,FBurnham is the new PM or not.
OL,12,FFor what it's worth, some of the
OL,13,Fcabinet believe it would be less
OL,14,Fchaotic if he sets the date for his
OL,15,Fexit, and he could use his time-
OL,16,Flimited period to shape a positive
OL,17,Flegacy for himself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779062581
OL,3,CStarmer 'deciding whether to announce
OL,4,Cdeparture timetable'
OL,6,FFor this contingent, like trade union
OL,7,Fleaders, the die is already cast that
OL,8,Fhe will have to resign in coming
OL,9,Fmonths, whether Burnham is elected an
OL,10,FMP or not. And the PM should
OL,11,Facknowledge that reality, they say.
OL,13,FOther ministers want him to stay,
OL,14,Fpointing out that there would be
OL,15,Fmayhem if Burnham were to lose and it
OL,16,Fwould be preferable in those
OL,17,Fcircumstances for the party to draw
OL,18,Fbreath rather than charge headlong
OL,19,Finto a leadership election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779062581
OL,3,CStarmer 'deciding whether to announce
OL,4,Cdeparture timetable'
OL,6,FMany of those insisting he shouldn't
OL,7,Fquit are also those who will be out of
OL,8,Fa job if Burnham or another candidate
OL,9,Freplaces him.
OL,11,FOne minister insists the choice is not
OL,12,Fso binary and there are other options
OL,13,Fthat could keep the government show on
OL,14,Fthe road.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779062581
OL,3,CStarmer 'deciding whether to announce
OL,4,Cdeparture timetable'
OL,6,FThis minister said, however, that
OL,7,Fwhatever Starmer decides he will have
OL,8,Fto spell this out explicitly and in
OL,9,Fdetail to all of us.
OL,11,FThe big personal judgment for Starmer
OL,12,Fis whether he becomes more or less of
OL,13,Fa lame duck by taking control of the
OL,14,Ftime and manner of his departure,
OL,15,Frather than leaving it in the lap of
OL,16,Fthe election gods.
OL,18,FHis colleagues don't know what he will
OL,19,Fdecide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
